VideoBam,is,a,free,video,hosting,service,that,allows,users,to,upload,videos,to,share,on,social,networking,sites,blogs,and,other,websites,The,VideoBam,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,data,and,functionality,of,VideoBam,into,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,accessing,user,information,retrieving,lists,of,videos,uploading,videos,deleting,videos,and,accessing,video,information